data.description: Back on the Market, the buyer's failure to get his loan approval. Gorgeous Home in Rowlett! New Flooring & Paint with soaring ceilings and lots of upgrades. Home With Full Standing Seam Metal Roof And Metal Siding. Hugh's family room with a view of the patio. The master bath has a marble floor & steps up to the jetted tub. Marble tile foyer, kit, hall & baths. Lots of cabinets & closet space. Huge corner lot, trees, ceiling fans, fireplace, sprinkle. Prefinished Metal Fence on Concrete Curb With Rear Rolling Gate. MUST SEE IT!!
